%h3.text-uppercase #{@brand.name} color palette
%p The Xaxis brand colors are inspired directly from the Xaxis logo. The color palette consists of 3 primary colors, 3 secondary colors and 3 neutral shades of gray.%h4.color-category Primary Colors
.row
  .col-md-4
    .color-card
      .color-card-top#dark-blue
      .color-card-bottom
        %h6.color-card-title Dark Blue
        %p.color-card-text.color-hex #3B6E8F
        %p.color-card-text rgb (59, 110, 143)
        %p.color-card-text CMYK (58, 17, 0, 46)

